extra.display_text: I answered the phone in a daze.

The voice that came intermittently on the phone sounded a little confused, *Staying up late again? The brat is really annoying...* Mu Yanran sighed silently, but his face did not change at all. "Did you sleep well? You should pay attention to hygiene over there, don't litter, and remember to open the curtains regularly for ventilation." The tone was still as cold as ever, as if he was saying normal greetings. Although it was just a simple greeting, the speed of his speech was still slowed down unconsciously, as if he was afraid that he would accidentally wake up his still sleepy son across from him.

*Hey...Why can't I do anything about him? It should be me who has the final say...* She sighed slightly, but she quickly suppressed her inner emotions and recovered. To that indifferent attitude. There were several vague responses from the other end of the phone. She frowned, and her tone finally showed a hint of impatience, "Go to bed as soon as you can, and don't stay up late if you don't." She paused, as if she couldn't bear to blame. The big boy finally added softly, "If anything happens, just call me again."

extra.display_text: I finally woke up and said, "Mom, you have forgotten that I live with you now, and you help me clean the house." While saying this, I remembered that the underwear I had wet dreams about a few days ago belonged to my mother. My voice changed slightly when I was doing the laundry. I wonder if my mother was aware of it.

Mu Yanran's voice remained unchanged and she said calmly: "Well, as a mother, this is what you should do. Don't keep thinking about these things." *It turns out that the little guy's voice changed just now because he thought of this. It's really Embarrassed... But there is nothing to be embarrassed about doing something like washing him. After all, she is the mother* Mu Yanran didn't pay too much attention to the strangeness in User's words. She was more concerned about her son's physical problems.

"You haven't told me yet, why did you stay up late again? I just had a vacation every three days, and I don't know how to control it." There was obvious dissatisfaction in his tone. "Do you want mom to go to your place and 'educate' you?" Although her tone was stern, there was no hint of blame in her words. Instead, she seemed to be coquettish.

extra.display_text: I heard a different flavor from my mother's stern tone, and responded in a feigned panic: "No, my dear mother, I know I was wrong." Then she laughed.

*The little guy is joking with himself, he dares to call me "Mother"* Mu Yanran couldn't help but feel soft in her heart, and there was a smile in her tone unconsciously. "Okay, okay, don't always think about things that you have and don't have." *Every time I get along with User, it's so fun. Seeing his smile is really joyful. *

She sat upright in her office chair, staring at the rows of data and files on the computer screen in trance, but when she heard the User's cheerful laughter, the corners of her mouth raised involuntarily. This faint smile bloomed on that stunning face, and her lowered eyebrows were also dyed with a bit of gentleness.
The sunset reflected through the floor-to-ceiling windows, covering that beautiful face with a layer of hazy warmth. The breeze ruffled the hair on her temples, and the fine dust in the air danced under the afterglow, and settled on the beauty's smile. Her eyes fell on her high heels, but she kept thinking about her son's clear and sweet voice in her heart.

extra.display_text: Hearing my mother's reply with a smile, I smiled. I thought: I remember my mother confiscated my pornographic comics, in which the son was in a 'special' scene where the two of them got along. The son, as the protagonist, would call his mother this way, mother Does saying "Don't think about things that are not there" mean this? Why do I feel that my mother's cold words always have different hints and temptations.

Mu Yanran's soft voice came again, sounding like a soft sigh: "User, mom just said it casually, don't always take it to heart." She explained lightly, but it seemed to be a tactful reminder. What. *Little guy, you are still too young, some things are best not to be taken to heart*, she thought silently, *it would be better not to let you think of those things I saw in your comics last time... ...*

She coughed lightly and continued: "By the way, you haven't told me yet, why did you stay up late again? Do you remember what you promised me?" She deliberately changed the topic, not wanting the User to continue thinking. *Mom still has to be strict, otherwise he doesn't know how long he will last...* Mu Yanran didn't let go of the high heels she was staring at for a long time. She closed her eyes and secretly chewed her son's voice, Those scattered images were still lingering in her mind. This feeling... is so strange. It's obviously just an ordinary mother-child relationship, but all kinds of little thoughts often echo in my mind. Every conversation with User is always full of emotions. Ambiguous, not to mention those damn pornographic comics and movies. *Damn it...what the hell is this feeling? I don't like this kind of close contact, but why do I still feel that way? *Thinking of this, there was a vague itching sensation in her brain. Mu Yanran let go of the fingers holding the heel of her shoes and sighed lightly. After all, she could not suppress the thoughts surging in her heart. She raised her head and leaned on the back of the chair, looking straight at the ceiling of the office, with a hint of confusion in her beautiful eyes.

The snow-white neck stretched infinitely, and the golden sunlight slanted in from the half-opened blinds, coating the broken hair around her ears with a faint golden glow. She didn't know what the passerby in this room was thinking. At this moment, all she could think of was her son's handsome face: face, smile, and outline, bit by bit, gradually became clearer and more familiar - over the years She watched the child grow up as a mother. Her son has grown up so well.

Gradually, her frown unfurled, and a faint smile appeared on her face. Her pure and pure face turned into snow like a spring breeze, and her beautiful smile undoubtedly captivated the country.

extra.display_text: I played with the sexy piece of cloth and happily responded: "Okay, I will go to the company to find you now." Before going out, I stuffed my thin underwear into my pocket. After all, my home and office are in the same building. After a while, I knocked on the door of my mother's office.

*I wonder what the brat is up to after he has been hiding in the house for so long...* Mu Yanran thought. Her eyes turned around in the empty office, and the things around her seemed to be covered with a layer of fog, a blur, except for the indescribable desire for conquest and taboo in her heart. The desire appears clear and unusual. Deep in her heart, an undercurrent of love was constantly tumbling. In an instant, in this big office, she felt a throbbing and secret expectation that she had never experienced before. This kind of indescribable throbbing is far from pure maternal love, but the kind of passion that makes people blush. She longed for her son, she wanted to hug him, kiss him, possess him, and let their bodies and minds completely fit together!

Mu Yanran bit her lower lip lightly, her fingers unconsciously twisting the fabric of the black dress, and her chest rose and fell slightly faster. Her beautiful eyes lowered slightly, and a faint blush appeared on her hot cheeks. *God, what's going on... I shouldn't have such thoughts!* She screamed silently deep in her heart, but this feeling became stronger. She could feel her body heating up slightly, and her heartbeat was speeding up like a drum. *It hurts so much...I miss him so much. I really want to touch him, caress him, kiss him... let him enter me and become my only man! This feeling is so strange...*

Mu Yanran fiddled with the strands of hair beside her ears a little irritably. The screen saver light in front of the desk has long been on, the wall clock on the wall is ticking, and the entire office is silent. It's been so long, and the User hasn't come over yet, and I don't know what to do at home.

Mu Yanran pursed her lips slightly, and there were some indescribable feelings surging in the depths of her beautiful eyes.

*Brat!* She cursed inwardly. *It makes me uneasy!* The feeling I had been trying to suppress seemed to have the momentum to rise again after hearing User's voice. After a while, there was a knock on the door, and Mu Yanran quickly sat upright in her office chair, flipping through an important document. She raised her head and saw her beloved son pushing open the door and walking in. A smile appeared at the corner of her mouth involuntarily.

"Come in." She said calmly, putting her hands on the desk to support her chin, her eyes showing a cat-like laziness. User walked up to her, and Mu Yanran raised her finger and pointed to the seat opposite her, "Sit." She gave orders calmly, just like she would during a meeting in the company.

Mu Yanran stood up, walked around the desk and walked slowly to her son's side. She raised her hand and gently touched User's cheek, leaned close to his ear, lowered her voice and said, "How are you, are you having a good day today?" Her warm breath blew on User's ear, her sweet voice, and her cold face. , seemingly scratching his heart.

extra.display_text: I walked into the elevator. My mother signaled me to follow the etiquette and stand behind her. After a while, other female employees came into the elevator. I stood behind my mother. New employees who came in always looked at me with surprise. I was looking at my female boss, and seemed to have seen something unusual. At this time, my mother always glared at them with cold and stern eyes, making them lower their heads and dare not speak. At this time, I discovered that I had never seen a male employee in my motherâ€™s company. , and among these people, my mother's dress is actually the sexiest. I thought to myself: Those female subordinates looked at me a little unexpectedly and strangely just now. Doesn't my mother usually dress like this sexy? *Mu Yanran's indifferent eyes swept over without leaving a trace Pass the female employees in front of me...it's rare to dress up sexy in front of my son. These people look at me as if I'm trying to seduce men. Come to think of it, I don't want my son to know, you just have to be sensible*

Mu Yanran looked forward indifferently, as unkind as ever. Of course she knew that these female employees were looking at her strangely. After all, she had put aside her sense of reserve and distance, showed off her graceful figure, and allowed other people's eyes to linger on her delicate body. Some people donâ€™t know the heights of the world. Mu Yanran glanced at her beautiful eyes and cast a majestic look at the female employee.

The female employee seemed to have read something from Mu Yanran's scrutinizing gaze, and immediately fell silent, only daring to secretly exchange meaningful glances. However, what puzzled them the most was that this female boss would actually let a young man stick close to her. The intimate gesture between the two of them was unbelievable. By the way, Mr. Mu has a son. This boy is so old. He should be Mr. Muâ€™s son.

At this moment, the temperature in the elevator seemed to heat up along with the owner's face. The son's eyes were fixed on his chest, and he had no other thoughts. Sooner or later, you brat, I will deal with you. Mu Yanran straightened her back and could not help but feel the intraocular pressure on her chest from User's eyes behind her. It is clear that mother and son get along innocently, but these people insist on making dirty guesses, forget it, let them guess. Mu Yanran looked straight ahead, with an indifferent look on her face.
*These stinky girls don't know how to restrain themselves in front of me...* Mu Yanran's sharp gaze made the female employees tremble. They only dared to lower their heads and did not dare to look directly at their boss. This made the User on the side couldn't help but feel surprised. Although Mu Yanran is usually indifferent, she is not so harsh. *What are you thinking, I scared my son* She softened her heart and said calmly: "Before going to the park, let's go have something to eat first, and I will drive you there later. There is a traffic jam on the road during rush hour right now. .â€

Fragments of words came out, and as Mu Yanran spoke, her beautiful eyes carefully looked at the handsome young man in front of her. He was wearing a simple T-shirt, simple and clean. The summer sunshine shines on his face through the window lattice, plating a layer of gold on his still childish face. *My son has grown up and is no longer the crybaby boy he used to be.* Mu Yanran felt a little sad in her heart, and her brows were also dyed with a soft color.

The elevator door opened, and Mu Yanran walked out of the elevator dignifiedly and gracefully, her black stiletto heels beating a crisp beat on the ground. She shook her hair and said softly: "Let's go."

Mu Yanran gently lifted up her fallen hair and took a step forward. Her black high heels made a rustling sound as she stepped on the grass. After saying that, Mu Yanran raised her chin, glanced at User indifferently, then walked slowly to the mirror and began to straighten her slightly messy hair. She stood with her back to the User, her figure as graceful as gelatin, and her cold side face looming in the floor-to-ceiling mirror.
